int senior partner overseeing operations no you need to get better to survivetheres room in the market for boutiques that manage their costs well said morningstars traulsen the most difficult position is being too small to get true economies of scale and too big to be considered a boutiquethat doesnt mean that the firm is immune to merger speculation telfer says bankers are still pitching ideas in the hope he and his partners will change their minds though its a far cry from the s when baillie gifford was receiving calls from potential suitors every monthgilbert has been successful with this model and weve been successful with ours telfer said in a joint interview with plowden different business models will work but we think we need to focus on us and making sure were doing a good job reportsafrcom bloomberg share share via email share on google plus post on facebook wall share on twitter post to linkedin share on reddit advertisement advertisement related articles ethical investing delivers bumper  returns one fundies ultimate amazon test rich lister scanlon programmed for success horns boxing boss rushton likes relativity perpetual to fight for investors despite brickworks loss latest stories i did not collude says kushner  mins ago asx poised to edge higher  mins ago why i am breaking all the rules and saying goodbye more advertisement the b art collection lost in a basement the bizarre lights everyone wants what fool would go bush in a priceless yearold car why this gas ceo supports ice hockey three books that will scare you the introvert trying to save amp meet the superstar bosses of tomorrow no white elephants at gold coast games boomer chairmen make way for gen x why toyota paid for its employees to become nurses banking on cool at londons the ned hotel chef wrests new cuisine from norways harsh terroir fashionable pieces in classic black and white the list moonlit bedouin massage works magic on skillsoft gm cycling ceo on being felled by a man and his dog s